Description: editorial PySide6 GUI for local pentesting with aircrack-ng
 WiFi Deauth Manager is an editorial Qt6 GUI that wraps aircrack-ng
 (airmon-ng, airodump-ng, aireplay-ng) with monitoring, focused scanning,
 JSON/CSV export, OUI vendor lookup and channel overlap analysis. It uses
 pkexec via polkit (auth_admin) for monitor-mode elevation and persists
 target names via XDG Base Directory (platformdirs).
 .
 Use this tool ONLY on networks you own or have explicit authorization to
 audit. Active attacks against third-party networks are illegal.
